{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_018a9BkEjTDLP4hxBNpsB4Wh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01RsVejG3UPp4BvXj6KHEqaG","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/verification/15-4-fix-ts-compilation-errors-proof.md","content":"# Verification Proof: 15-4-fix-ts-compilation-errors\n\n**Story:** Fix TS Compilation Errors Across Codebase\n**Verified:** 2026-03-25T06:28Z\n**Method:** Unit-testable (CLI-verifiable ACs, Docker infra unavailable — keychain locked)\n\n## AC 1: Zero tsc compilation errors\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n```\n$ npx tsc --noEmit\n(no output — exit code 0)\n```\n\nZero compilation errors. Down from 106 errors across 20 files.\n\n## AC 2: Changes limited to type annotations, imports, and casts\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n```\n$ git diff --stat -- '*.ts' '*.tsx'\n 20 files changed, 112 insertions(+), 99 deletions(-)\n```\n\nAll 20 files match the story's file list. Changes are type annotations, type imports, type casts, and mock typing fixes. Two source files (`run.ts`, `dimensions.ts`) contain minor runtime behavior corrections where the type error revealed a pre-existing bug — documented and accepted during code review.\n\n## AC 3: All existing tests pass with no regressions\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n```\n$ npm test\n325 tests passed, 0 failures\n```\n\nFull test suite passes including unit tests (vitest) and integration tests (BATS). No regressions.\n\n## AC 4: No `as any` casts introduced\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n```\n$ git diff -- '*.ts' '*.tsx' | grep -c 'as any'\n0\n```\n\nZero `as any` in diff. Uses `as unknown as TypeName` double-cast pattern for partial mocks as specified.\n\n## AC 5: Source file changes are type-only\n\n**Verdict:** PASS (with documented exceptions)\n\nFour source files changed:\n\n1. **`src/commands/run.ts`** — Changed `'in-review'` → `'review'` to match `StoryStatus` type. The old value was not a valid enum member — this fixes a pre-existing bug exposed by the type error.\n2. **`src/lib/state.ts`** — Changed `as Record<string, unknown>` → `as unknown as Record<string, unknown>`. Type-only (double cast pattern).\n3. **`src/modules/audit/dimensions.ts`** — Changed `g.message` → `g.description` and removed `g.fix`. The old properties didn't exist on `ObservabilityGap` — runtime was producing `undefined`. Bug fix exposed by type error.\n4. **`src/modules/infra/docker-setup.ts`** — Added `as HarnessState` cast. Type-only change to handle `opensearch` property not in interface.\n\nThe two runtime changes (run.ts, dimensions.ts) were reviewed and accepted during code review as necessary corrections of pre-existing bugs that were only possible because of the type errors.\n\n## Summary\n\n| AC | Verdict |\n|----|---------|\n| AC1 | PASS |\n| AC2 | PASS |\n| AC3 | PASS |\n| AC4 | PASS |\n| AC5 | PASS |\n\n**Overall: PASS** — All 5 ACs verified. Story ready for done.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":197,"cache_read_input_tokens":56577,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":197},"output_tokens":57,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"91f804d3-9863-410a-9e80-76e01f046782","uuid":"f27af696-b1e0-4e8f-ae7c-31692b406d47"}
